name: QUICKIE004 (dog bed dog)
description:
An original Gory Orgy mini-loop. 4 seconds. 2304X2304, H264, 2021
QUICKIE004 is a multi-layered animation that utilises more than one machine-learning model. A frenzied, shape-shifting couple (AI-generated erotica) is conspicuously analysed by a machine-learning model that identifies people and objects. QUICKIE004 is one of 25. One copy is retained by the artist, while the other 24 are available for purchase. Gory Orgy is the experimental machine-learning project by kiwi artist and film-maker Ed Lust.
